w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-squire">约翰·斯奎尔 (John Squire)</a>宣布了期待已久的合作项目细节，首支单曲“Just Another Rainbow”将于下个月发布。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/liam-gallagher-oasis-reunion-tour-noel-interview-2020-new-album-2615869"><em>NME</em>大读物 – Liam Gallagher：“绿洲团聚很快就会发生”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>主唱转型为独唱明星，以及前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stone-roses">Stone Roses</a>吉他手转型为艺术家，他们在一起玩音乐已经有一段时间了。早在 6 月，Gallagher 在他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-live-in-knebworth-kasabian-amyl-sniffers-3239799">Knebworth 演出</a>中就邀请了 Squires 表演 1995 年 Oasis 经典歌曲“Champagne Supernova”，然后发推文：“超级组合即将到来 LG JS。”</p><p>加拉格尔还<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-confirms-he-and-the-stone-roses-john-squire-are-in-supergroup-talks-3314922">确认两人“肯定”会合作，</a>然后调侃说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-teases-joint-album-with-john-squire-as-the-best-record-since-the-beatles-revolver-3520505">两人的联合唱片将是“自《左轮手枪》以来最好的唱片”</a> ，指的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>的第七张专辑。</p><p>现在，加拉格尔和斯奎尔 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-and-john-squire-tease-joint-album-3560558">本周</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-and-john-squire-tease-joint-album-3560558">推出了一个网站，发布了一系列彼此的视频</a>，并宣布他们的第一首单曲“Just Another Rainbow”将于 2024 年 1 月 5 日发行，“随着这一年的展开，将会有更多新音乐推出” ”。该单曲可在 7 英寸黑胶唱片上预订并<a href="https://gallaghersquire.lnk.to/JustAnotherRainbow" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预先保存。</p><p>听听下面的单曲片段。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C1HG0cWNqIW/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.3